{
  "stem": "25834.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because, this time, I saw a big different, very big different between equipment and manpower, between German and Soviet and Poland either.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The German was very superior equipped and was prepared to the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And still, we was try go around the German, not go directly and face, because we was in uniform.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I change couple things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "For example, in the-- try be civil not a military guy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we reach Warsaw, both with some small problems.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I saw my family in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And, you know, that was for me very exciting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, you see this was everything prepare the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Polish people was, you know, try build good feeling, be prepare for war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, you know, that was very hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Germany was big power.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know how was the powerful German Army if English, French, Belgium, Norwegian, et cetera, cannot do nothing?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Poland was the same. you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In other words, Polish people was not prepare to do war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And probably, Poland be fighting longer, only the Soviet kill the reconstruction the army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we going back, back, back, I mean Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the east was natural cover for army, was waters and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] places where you can cover, and the trees and something like this.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from the west, only the Soviet went to Poland and kill everybody and sent right away-- arrested and sent to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was very, very sad feeling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thus we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] thus we, you know, not like the Soviet, because these are people who trade everything and everybody.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The family situation-- you see, during the war, Warsaw was bombarded by German artillery in 1939 and also the airplane.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many, many people was without the home, because was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
